---
title: Seasoned Chicken & Roast Veggie Couscous with Toasted Almonds & Garlic Dip
description: South American seasoning, brown sugar and lemon combine to give chicken an irresistible flavour boost. Perched on a bed of tender
roast veggies and fluffy couscous, then topped with a garlicky sauce, this has something for everyone.

